{"tid":532713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Fire and Fury作者：梅鐸稱鄧文迪是中國間諜","createTime":"2018-01-18T06:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T09:18:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6dc90da828049a0459f34a630eb2e840ea598ef7","tid":532713,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1990000/1992336/0117001_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1990000%2F1992336%2F0117001_1024.jpg&h=d66ab985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美諜影重重。繼有美媒揭露，反間諜官員曾提醒總統特朗普女婿兼高級顧問庫什納，警剔媒體大亨梅鐸的前妻鄧文迪後，大爆特朗普政府內幕的新書《Fire and Fury：Inside the Trump White House》的作者在Twitter表示，梅鐸曾多次透露，其前妻是中國間諜。<br />\n<br />\n《Fire and Fury》作者、美國記者沃爾夫（Michael Wolff）周二（16日）在Twitter表示，梅鐸離婚後，曾多次告訴那些肯聽得進去的人說，鄧文迪是中國間諜，從結婚開始就是。<br />\n<br />\n49歲的鄧文迪有傳奇華裔女子之稱，生於山東濟南，父親是一家工廠的負責人，她於1988年到美國讀書，曾在耶魯大學商學院學習，後來在香港的Star TV工作，期間遇見母公司新聞集團（News Corp.）的創辦人梅鐸。<br />\n<br />\n鄧文迪1999年與梅鐸結婚，是梅鐸的第三任妻子，據報鄧文迪婚後曾幫助新聞集團在中國安排了一些交易，並與江澤民等高層政治人物會面。鄧的發言人表示，她有時與梅鐸前往中國，但淡化了她在商業往來中扮演的角色。<br />\n<br />\n2013年，鄧文迪與梅鐸結束14年的婚姻。曾有報道稱，她離婚前與英國前首相布萊爾有曖昧關係，雙方否認；離婚後，又曾傳出鄧文迪搭上俄羅斯總統普京，克里姆林宮和鄧文迪也否認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1990000/1992336/0116001_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1990000%2F1992336%2F0116001_1024.jpg&h=78022814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日美國《華爾街日報》（WSJ）引述知情人士透露，美國反間諜官員曾提醒庫什納，鄧文迪可能利用與他夫婦倆的好友關係，推進中國政府的利益；當局又擔憂，鄧文迪涉及中國在美的億元園林項目的遊說。<br />\n<br />\n不過，鄧文迪與庫什納和其妻子伊萬卡，均未被指控有任何不當行為。鄧文迪方面亦否認知曉任何由中國政府出資的園林項目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://china.hket.com/article/1992336/美國新書《Fire%20and%20Fury》作者：梅鐸曾稱鄧文迪是中國間諜\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1992336%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%B0%E6%9B%B8%E3%80%8AFire%2520and%2520Fury%E3%80%8B%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%EF%BC%9A%E6%A2%85%E9%90%B8%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E9%84%A7%E6%96%87%E8%BF%AA%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C&d=K57mQQZxUvxwTeepu0IeDJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e272419a\" target=\"_blank\">http://china.hket.com/article/1992336/美國新書《Fire%20and%20Fury》作者：梅鐸曾稱鄧文迪是中國間諜</a>"},{"pid":"e24e4d35bda75072423dc3820cd74bc263580161","tid":532713,"uid":25424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"睇怕Facebook都一鳩樣"},{"pid":"7141b0cf307aa6468a762e44dc5e6318b484bb80","tid":532713,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"點解d鬼佬係中意呢d樣嘅東方女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野審美觀"},{"pid":"6639b3ff016d2e0173e2bbfa6747754fa09cb69e","tid":532713,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7141b0cf307aa6468a762e44dc5e6318b484bb80","tid":532713,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"點解d鬼佬係中意呢d樣嘅東方女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野審美觀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"好屌"},{"pid":"5ee031757591059957812a5cd52e6adb55c0493e","tid":532713,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7141b0cf307aa6468a762e44dc5e6318b484bb80","tid":532713,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"點解d鬼佬係中意呢d樣嘅東方女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野審美觀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"好似話意女人有少少顏色同細細粒?"},{"pid":"b0e387c8310f15c4b0edd4f5f859389851f48bdc","tid":532713,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockqu